title: Daily Motivation
description: A Twitter/X bot that gives motivational quotes everyday and polls the users of Twitter/X to collect statistics in Postgres which gets tweeted at teh end of every week.

title: Data Scraping via Twitter/X
description: An automation script that uses OpenCV and AI to filter tweets through specific conditions and attempts to interact with them in some form.

title: Overseer
description: A Discord bot that has the ability to convert various forms of user input into their respective Linear Regression models.
